name: Plywood Print Blocks
description:
These plywood screen printed blocks are approximately 125 x 125 x 36 mm and are provided with different artwork on each side.  Artwork is selected from our greeting card designs and we usually print artwork from the same range on both sides.  To view available designs, view our greeting card designs on this website.  That said, if you would like particular artwork from different ranges just email us and we can accommodate your needs.  To email Studio Antic just click on the contact button on the info panel.

Oh by the way, THESE PRINT BLOCKS LOOK GREAT ON A MANTELPIECE, and you can turn them around occasionally for a different look.

These print blocks are varnished with a water based varnish and whilst we try to maintain stock levels please allow 1-2 weeks for delivery.
